longBusinessSummary: Heimstaden AB (publ) owns, develops, and manages residential properties in Sweden, Germany, Denmark, the Netherlands, the Czech Republic, Norway, Finland, the United Kingdom, and Poland. The company was founded in 2004 and is based in Malmö, Sweden. Heimstaden AB (publ) is a subsidiary of Fredensborg AS.
